{"tid":38624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發現公司用翻版軟件,求舉報教學","createTime":"2016-12-14T05:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T18:03:07.000Z","uid":65395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32567e30c544971822eee8da3e95cc959a0d0ea2","tid":38624,"uid":65395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:00:15.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過舉報,海關有冇獎金?<br />\n出年冇人工加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,唯有靠呢筆錢生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba8dbf3b1b70a07c82b19a9bdeec4f95ac72059","tid":38624,"uid":16554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:04:48.000Z","msg":"舉報公司好似有好多獎金"},{"pid":"8b899f9a2ede7778f141bf9d092a8209ea88b520","tid":38624,"uid":65395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:05:45.000Z","msg":"定係要搵有關既軟件公司舉報?<br />\n定係香港已經無人理呢樣野?支那化?"},{"pid":"7aaa97a9e6fc6fe4d863eb31622852710b90bacb","tid":38624,"uid":65395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:08:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舉報公司好似有好多獎金</blockquote><br />\n求過來人教學!<br />\n係咪要搜證, 但呢樣野要我做埋海關做咩?<br />\n同埋會唔會告尻埋我? 我唔想用嫁 屌你老細 食屎喇"},{"pid":"99e057a7f086281137576fb87bf5618bcff97620","tid":38624,"uid":65395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:40:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7cd5d57263bdee4b52b47d32691e9e8e4a31da4","tid":38624,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T06:10:15.000Z","msg":"舉報計劃<br />\n為協助政府保護知識產權，知識產權業界設立了五項舉報獎賞計劃，由海關負責管理。任何人如向海關提供資料，導致成功制止侵犯知識產權罪行，並且檢獲若干數量的盜版或偽冒貨物，便可獲發賞金。<br />\n<br />\n該五項舉報獎賞計劃為：<br />\n<br />\n反盜版獎賞計劃（由版權業撥款資助）；<br />\n反冒牌藥及假藥獎賞計劃（由香港科研製藥聯會撥款資助）；<br />\n打擊非法複印書本及期刊獎賞計劃（由香港版權影印授權協會撥款資助）；<br />\n打擊非法複製報章及雜誌獎賞計劃（由香港複印授權協會撥款資助）；以及<br />\n打擊公司使用盜版軟件獎賞計劃（由BSA | 軟件聯盟撥款資助）。<br />\n舉報方法：<br />\n<br />\n舉報熱線（24小時）<br />\n(852) 2545 6182<br />\n傳真<br />\n(852) 2543 4942；或<br />\n郵寄<br />\n海關關長<br />\n香港郵政總局郵政信箱1166號<br />\n所有提供線報人仕資料皆絕對保密。<br />\n<br />\n打咗去先啦"},{"pid":"65fb03fe7e2e53d78d1b8e8cba5e6da8b63d402d","tid":38624,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T06:12:28.000Z","msg":"篤灰係江湖大忌"},{"pid":"7cd945179c9e983124de1147a2a1b4142e2c744b","tid":38624,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T06:17:47.000Z","msg":"搭單問 舉報黑工有冇獎金 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622cef7bf6e10d4c50a5c3c022563ab58c9d0cf1","tid":38624,"uid":65395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:03:38.000Z","msg":"舉報要準備咩資料 就咁比個公司名咁兒戲？ 咁我好多個名喎， 另外點收獎金 過數定開票"},{"pid":"2e5b77797231b8b20c0c67bd4f9988b2976f399f","tid":38624,"uid":65395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:07:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>篤灰係江湖大忌</blockquote><br />\n無人識我 只係小員工 無所謂啦"},{"pid":"8b59fd92455e9b25d84530c9b602b8c2a7938e54","tid":38624,"uid":12013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:09:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>篤灰係江湖大忌</blockquote><br />\n無人識我 只係小員工 無所謂啦</blockquote><br />\n一路好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f352f77e7441bc96410a2b1e1467ad233e3603","tid":38624,"uid":65395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:14:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>篤灰係江湖大忌</blockquote><br />\n無人識我 只係小員工 無所謂啦</blockquote><br />\n一路好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩意思"},{"pid":"3ab056e2c1371e2fcc34d937101b2be85967ad4a","tid":38624,"uid":2416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:16:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquo